Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.50,0:01:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,[Kyosuke Higuchi] Then, once you're\Nfully convinced that I'm the real thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.50,0:01:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,-you and I can get married.\N-[gasping]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.46,0:01:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, based on what he said,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.75,0:01:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Higuchi is Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.42,0:01:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,GUIDANCE
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.97,0:01:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[tense music playing]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.69,0:01:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] If the killing of criminals stops now,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.98,0:01:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,then there's no doubt that Higuchi\Nis the one with Kira's powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.53,0:01:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.24,0:01:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew that Amane would do\Nalmost anything for Light Yagami, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.11,0:02:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,but to think she would\Nactually go this far?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.91,0:02:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,If criminals do stop dying after this\Nit will make it difficult to determine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.75,0:02:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,a critical element:\NHow Kira conducts his murders.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.63,0:02:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to think of a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.04,0:02:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Misa, how did you get Higuchi to confess?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.55,0:02:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Easy. That guy is totally in love with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.22,0:02:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,All I had to do was tell him\NI'd marry him if he was really Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.43,0:02:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus, I managed to convince him\Nthat I'm the second Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.18,0:02:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa Amane] If I didn't say this now,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.85,0:02:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd probably end up\Ncontradicting my story later.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.98,0:02:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Misa, you idiot!\NDidn't I tell you to deny all that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.86,0:02:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa]\NBut now we know Higuchi is Kira, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.57,0:02:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,So what's the problem?\NCan't we just catch him?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.61,0:02:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose this is what you would call\Na victory, right? Matsuda?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.20,0:02:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.41,0:02:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But right now, we still don't know exactly\Nhow he kills his victims, do we.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.25,0:02:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's what I was thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.37,0:02:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Before we move to arrest Higuchi,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.71,0:02:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to find out how he kills people.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.55,0:02:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,If the criminals stop dying,\Nwe'll be able to figure it out,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.17,0:02:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,unless we come up with another idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.97,0:03:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.47,0:03:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. At any rate,\Neven if we do arrest Higuchi,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.51,0:03:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,we're not going to do it
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.72,0:03:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,until we're certain\Nthat criminals have stopped dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.98,0:03:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me think about this for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.94,0:03:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,-[L] Wedy.\N-[Wedy] Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.94,0:03:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,An update on the current situation,\Nplease.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.28,0:03:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,[Wedy]\NEverything's going smoothly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.82,0:03:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We should be able to track 70%\Nof their movements
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.36,0:03:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,using our cameras\Ninside the office building.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.20,0:03:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[L]\NWhat about outside of the office?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.03,0:03:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not going to be possible\Nwith just Watari and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.37,0:03:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What if you just focus solely on Higuchi?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.71,0:03:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Higuchi?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.21,0:03:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I've only been able to enter the houses\Nof five of the men, so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.17,0:03:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But Mido, Namikawa and Higuchi's\Nall have super high tech security systems.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.30,0:03:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially Higuchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.01,0:03:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,He recently constructed a dampening room\Nthat shuts out any electronic waves.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.72,0:03:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It took me two days\Njust to break into the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.27,0:03:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,This guy sure does sound suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.31,0:03:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm. All right. Then begin installing\Nmicrophones, trackers, and cameras.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.52,0:03:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But not in the house.\NInstead just put them in every car.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.03,0:04:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,[Wedy] What? After getting this far?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.65,0:04:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know how difficult it is\Nto get break into someone's house?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.66,0:04:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, do you have any idea\Nhow many cars this guy has?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.33,0:04:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] He has six.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.45,0:04:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine then. I just have to install them\Nin all his cars, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.21,0:04:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.04,0:04:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa] Oh, if Higuchi had been bugged\Nearlier, I would have been in big trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.43,0:04:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] Light, I'm sorry\Nto keep coming back to this topic...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.98,0:04:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just get right to the point...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.81,0:04:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.52,0:04:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember?\NKilling anyone, I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.94,0:04:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.15,0:04:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,[upset] Are you still going on about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.36,0:04:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, I'm not Kira. How many times do I--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.66,0:04:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want you to answer the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.53,0:04:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, do you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.87,0:04:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.41,0:04:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Misa, what about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.83,0:04:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't remember.\NHow could I, because I'm not Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.63,0:05:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, Light. Please listen to\Nwhat I'm about to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.47,0:05:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like you to thoroughly analyze\Nmy current theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.30,0:05:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,This could determine the way\Nin which we end up catching Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.39,0:05:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] Light Yagami used to be Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.06,0:05:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Kira's power has somehow\Npassed on to another person.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.15,0:05:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Light Yagami now has no memory\Nof ever being Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.49,0:05:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I need your analysis,\Nbased on these assumptions.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.11,0:05:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think you can do that for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.12,0:05:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Yeah, I'll give it a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.95,0:05:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] Light Yagami used to be Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.16,0:05:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Kira's power has somehow been passed on\Nto another person.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.38,0:05:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that because Light Yagami\Nwanted that to happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.96,0:05:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Or was there someone else\Nin control of Light,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.42,0:05:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,lurking in the background,\Nwho gave him the power?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.30,0:05:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it that person who passed\NLight's powers to someone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.69,0:06:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Given your premise,\Nit would be my will.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.66,0:06:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.37,0:06:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,If there is a third party with the ability\Nto bestow or transfer Kira's power,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.91,0:06:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,and they didn't want their method\Nto be discovered,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.04,0:06:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It makes no sense\Nthat they would wait so long
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.00,0:06:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,to transfer it from you to the next Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.80,0:06:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,If we believe that this was the work\Nof some being, watching us from above,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.76,0:06:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,then we'd have to accept\Nthat they are impossible to catch.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.76,0:06:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to mention that I'd already be dead,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.39,0:06:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,or at the very least I'm being made\Nto be a fool
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.02,0:06:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,by eternally dancing in the palm\Nof someone's hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.90,0:06:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's highly unlikely\Nthat such a being exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.98,0:06:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] Even if Light Yagami was Kira…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.82,0:06:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Kira's power can only be transferred by\Nthe will of the person who possesses it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.58,0:06:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Light. I can now say\Nthat I feel 99 percent better.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.17,0:07:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll create a situation where Higuchi
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.26,0:07:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,will not be able\Nto pass on his power to anyone else
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.05,0:07:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have him show us\Nhow he kills.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.43,0:07:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.97,0:07:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] I'm going to trick Higuchi\Nusing Sakura TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.64,0:07:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,-Like a hidden camera show!\N-[Misa] What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.19,0:07:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] We'll use The Kira Special\Nthat Demegawa airs every week.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.82,0:07:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll book a three hour time slot.\NIt'll be announced that Kira's identity
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.86,0:07:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,will be revealed\Nnear the end of the special.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.70,0:07:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Would anyone actually buy that, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.66,0:07:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Sakura TV, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.87,0:07:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,[Matsuda] For all we know,\NHiguchi might not even watch that program.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.62,0:07:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll get Namikawa to call him\Nand say
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.83,0:07:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,"This is bad. Turn on your TV."\NThat should be enough to get him watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.88,0:07:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Higuchi will buy it once he\Nrealizes that the special guest on TV
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.34,0:07:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,is someone who knows his secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.76,0:07:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I get it.\NSo, we'll be using Aiber, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.72,0:08:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[Matsuda]\NHe'll reveal that he was a spy all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.56,0:08:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm afraid you're incorrect.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.44,0:08:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We will not be using Aiber.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.36,0:08:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] Whoever appears on the show...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.69,0:08:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,has to be someone who Higuchi believes\Nhe'll be able to kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.57,0:08:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] In other words, it has to be someone\Nwhose name he can look up easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.83,0:08:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But we're never going to find\Na person like that, are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.41,0:08:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[everyone] Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.12,0:08:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-You're the only one who can do it.\N-Matsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.83,0:08:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Matsuda.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.13,0:08:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Higuchi probably thinks that\Nyou were listening in on their meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.75,0:08:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and overheard their plans\Nto kill people.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.92,0:08:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] It would make sense that\NMisa's manager, who he thought was dead,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.55,0:08:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,-is the one revealing his secret.\N-That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.10,0:08:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have Sakura TV use a voice filter\Nand frosted glass
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.47,0:08:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,to protect your identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.35,0:08:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Higuchi will probably realize from\Nthe announcement and the silhouette
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.52,0:08:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,that it's the manager, Taro Matsui.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.31,0:08:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] And just to make sure,\Nwe'll have the studio mess up
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.03,0:08:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and accidentally reveal your face\Nfrom behind the frosted glass.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.32,0:08:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! Sounds exciting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.61,0:08:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] Until the show ends, the announcer\Nwill keep saying they'll reveal
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.62,0:09:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,the full name of H,\Nwho's acting as Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.91,0:09:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Higuchi would feel cornered.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.41,0:09:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,He'd have no choice but to find out\Nthe manager's name as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.08,0:09:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We can anticipate what actions he'll take.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.88,0:09:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll witness his killing method.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.21,0:09:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,After that, we arrest him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.88,0:09:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,There is one potential problem\Nwith this plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.39,0:09:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,If Higuchi can kill\Nby simply looking at someone's face,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.22,0:09:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,just like the second Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.31,0:09:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,-Matsuda will die.\N-[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.81,0:09:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But, considering the fact\Nthat you're still alive,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.44,0:09:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and how he's pursuing Misa,\NI doubt that's the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.03,0:09:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] At any rate,\Nwe're only going to do this
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.99,0:09:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,once criminals stop dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.49,0:09:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have to wait for two or three days\Nto see whether or not that happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.87,0:09:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[L] In the meantime,\NMatsuda will have to decide
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.79,0:09:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,if he wants to go through\Nwith this plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.04,0:09:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.42,0:09:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[Matsuda] I don't need two or three days\Nto decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.88,0:09:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.24,0:10:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[Reiji Namikawa] Well I'm here.\NWhat's with this private meeting?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.37,0:10:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Namikawa, tell me,\Nwho do you think is Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.92,0:10:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[scoffs]\NWhy do you want to know what I think?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.71,0:10:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, for all I know,\Nit could be you, Shimura.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.13,0:10:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Or maybe even Mido.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.09,0:10:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimura can't be Kira,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.93,0:10:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,he was the one who came crying to me
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.72,0:10:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,about how he can't go along\Nwith Kira's crimes anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.39,0:10:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? But if Mido had turned out\Nto be Kira, you would have been killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.39,0:10:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you and Mido would have\Nbeen successful on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.48,0:10:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way either of you would need\Nto hold those stupid meetings,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.15,0:10:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,let alone with seven others.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.61,0:11:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[Shimura] I can at least see that much.\NWe're all cooperating with these killings
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.70,0:11:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,because we're afraid\Nof Kira turning on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.99,0:11:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean it's only a matter of time\Nuntil the public finds out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.37,0:11:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And this isn't going to stop\Nuntil that happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.92,0:11:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Shimura, let me ask you then.\NWho do you think Kira might be?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.51,0:11:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Takahashi or Higuchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.34,0:11:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Takahashi is just a decoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.51,0:11:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Kira would make sure\Nthere are people less clever than him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.43,0:11:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh. Well then it looks like\Nwe all know the truth already.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.77,0:11:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,[Namikawa] It's Higuchi, isn't it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.60,0:11:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, he's the one who's most obsessed\Nwith money and success.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.07,0:11:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He might always act like\Nhe's not interested in those things,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.11,0:11:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,but that just proves it all the more.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.40,0:11:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And he always insults everyone around him\Nand can't use his people well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.58,0:11:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe that's why he was demoted
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.45,0:11:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,from being head of\Nthe development department.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.95,0:11:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, I meant to ask,\Nwas I the only one you invited here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.12,0:11:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,[Shingo Mido] I also invited Ooi, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.42,0:11:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,but he said, "You can hold your stupid,\Nprivate meetings by yourself."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.84,0:12:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,-Go figure.\N-[Namikawa] Ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.51,0:12:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Good old Ooi,\Nalways the blunt one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.72,0:12:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,[Mido] We can also rule out Kida\Nas a possible suspect,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.60,0:12:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,as he was the one who provided\Nthe account for funds
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.18,0:12:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,in order to commission Coil.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.85,0:12:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Namikawa, during that first meeting\Nafter Hatori died,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.48,0:12:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,you got a call on your cell phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.23,0:12:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wondering who it was from.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.07,0:12:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm, you know, Shimura,\Nyou're really are a sharp one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.61,0:12:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Kira probably selected you\Nbecause he appreciates your caution.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.45,0:12:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,[phone rings]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.95,0:12:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,[Namikawa] Hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.45,0:12:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Namikawa speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.62,0:12:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's L.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.00,0:12:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,-Before I go on, are you by yourself?\N-No.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.38,0:12:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Then just act like\Nit's a normal call again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.55,0:12:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think there's any need for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.26,0:12:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,One of the people here with me\Nwas just expressing his suspicions
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.43,0:12:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,about your last phone call.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.05,0:12:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is that on the line? Namikawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.93,0:12:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,-It's L.\N-[gasping]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.10,0:12:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,L, Mido and Shimura are here as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.27,0:12:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm reasonably certain\Nthat neither of them are Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.61,0:13:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, they seem fed up with it\Nat this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.98,0:13:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll speak for them and say\Nthey choose to stand back
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.15,0:13:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and watch your face-off with Kira,\Nlike I plan to.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.95,0:13:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm. That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.32,0:13:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Tonight, I'm going to catch Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.79,0:13:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'll need a favor from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.75,0:13:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[Namikawa] Hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.16,0:13:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it's the end for Higuchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.04,0:13:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You know that it's him?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.96,0:13:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha! So even the great L\Ncan be tricked.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.38,0:13:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Based on your reaction,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.55,0:13:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm now a hundred percent certain\Nthat Higuchi is Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.47,0:13:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Namikawa is pretty smart, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.55,0:13:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But then I always thought he was,\Nfrom looking at his face.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.06,0:13:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess this proves it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.31,0:13:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that was just because Light messed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.85,0:13:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm baiting Higuchi\Nwith a staged TV special tonight,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.19,0:13:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakura TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.98,0:13:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] A few minutes into the program,\NI want you to contact Higuchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.32,0:13:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell him to tune in.\NDo that for me
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.82,0:13:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,and I won't go after you\Nor any of the other five.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.70,0:13:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,If the others, Kida, Takahashi,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.87,0:13:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and Ooi if they try to do anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.00,0:13:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,make sure to stop them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.54,0:13:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.34,0:14:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems it really was Higuchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.09,0:14:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll be captured tonight, apparently.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.13,0:14:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.84,0:14:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been about three days\Nsince I stopped killing criminals.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.01,0:14:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That should be good enough,\Nshouldn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.73,0:14:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, when I marry Misa Amane,\NThe Second Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.23,0:14:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have the Shinigami eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.44,0:14:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,With that power in my hands,\NYotsuba will be under my control.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.69,0:14:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughs maniacally]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.91,0:14:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[phone rings]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.74,0:14:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Higuchi, we've got a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.33,0:14:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Turn on the television.\NCheck out Sakura TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.33,0:14:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[Higuchi] Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.04,0:14:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,KIRA'S IDENTITY
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.04,0:14:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[MC] So, you're saying\None of those people is Kira, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.17,0:14:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[Matsuda, voice disguised] Yes. I've got\Na lot of evidence to prove it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.22,0:14:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.76,0:14:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, it's probably a hoax.\NThis is Sakura TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.64,0:14:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[Namikawa] No, it's more than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.14,0:14:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,At the beginning of the show\Nhe said he overheard
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.14,0:14:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,a meeting,\Nbetween eight people.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.10,0:15:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,[Higuchi] What?\NSomeone who knows about the meetings?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.52,0:15:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is it? Did someone betray us?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.02,0:15:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,[Matsuda] One of them was killed by Kira\Nand now there are only seven left.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.57,0:15:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The man who died was Mr. H.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.95,0:15:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,[Higuchi]\NMr. H? Hatori…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.36,0:15:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,If he knows this much,\Nhe could be one of the other six.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.41,0:15:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,No, maybe it's Coil?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.08,0:15:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,[Matsuda] Mr. H wanted to leave\Nthe meetings
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.04,0:15:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and was killed by Kira because of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.54,0:15:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[Higuchi] No, it can't be any\Nof the others,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.38,0:15:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,there's no benefit for them\Nto do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.67,0:15:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But no one else knows about the meetings,\Ndo they?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.17,0:15:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it, who is it?\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.09,0:15:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.93,0:15:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,-[scraping sound]\N-[Matsuda winces]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.47,0:15:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's-- it’s him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.22,0:15:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[clamoring]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.31,0:15:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Misa's manager.\NMatsui, that's his name.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.40,0:15:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is he still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.73,0:15:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[Namikawa] He explained earlier\Nthat he thought he was going to be killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.65,0:15:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,He pretended to fall out of\Nthe apartment window
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.74,0:15:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and escaped to a balcony\Na few floors below.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.70,0:15:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[Higuchi] That can't be.\NJust to be careful, I went home that night
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.37,0:16:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and wrote his name in the notebook\Nlike it was written on his business card.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.50,0:16:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,TARO MATSUI
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.46,0:16:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[Higuchi] Why is he still alive then?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.88,0:16:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Could he be a former entertainer\Nwho became a manager
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.00,0:16:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,using his stage name?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.88,0:16:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.47,0:16:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If that weren't bad enough,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.63,0:16:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,he said that he continued\Nto investigate Yotsuba up until now
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.55,0:16:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and he's figured out\Nwhich one of us is Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.14,0:16:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm contacting everyone right now\Nto let them know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.97,0:16:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. We'll talk later.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.69,0:16:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,[MC] Sir, we are terribly sorry\Nfor that accident. Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.02,0:16:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We can stop if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.77,0:16:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[Matsuda] No. I knew I was going to be\Nin danger going into this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.86,0:16:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,This is for the sake of justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.61,0:16:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'll see it through to the end\Neven if it means my death.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.32,0:16:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,[man] Yeah, that's perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.33,0:16:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, just be sure to hold off on
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.20,0:16:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,the Kira announcement\Nuntil the last minute, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.12,0:16:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,[Higuchi]\NI have to kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.21,0:16:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down. Misa knows his face,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.67,0:16:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,so if she's the Second Kira,\Nshe should know what his real name is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.55,0:16:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[phone beeps]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.63,0:16:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[phone rings]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.05,0:16:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.89,0:17:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,-[busy signal]\N-[Higuchi groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.56,0:17:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.02,0:17:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[Matsuda] To be honest,\NI've been debating
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.73,0:17:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,for a long time whether or not\NI should make this announcement.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.23,0:17:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But now that I'm here, I know I've done\Nthe right thing in coming forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.11,0:17:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.48,0:17:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows\Nwhen they'll make the announcement
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.24,0:17:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,[MC] ...Kira's identity will be\Nannounced soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.78,0:17:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[phone rings]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.78,0:17:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,[voice-over on TV]\NCosme Misa.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.28,0:17:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,-A devilish charm, an angel's glitter…\N-[Misa giggles on-screen]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.66,0:17:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Misa's new line of lipstick.\NJust for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.71,0:17:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Mido, it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.96,0:17:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you watching Sakura TV?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.58,0:17:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you call your father\Nat the House of Councilors.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.17,0:17:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Have him pulls some strings\Nat the Ministry of Internal Affairs
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.01,0:17:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,to stop this broadcast.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.09,0:17:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm watching but I don't think\Nwe could stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.55,0:17:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,[Mido] No one believes this program
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.05,0:17:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,so we'd only make ourselves\Nlook suspicious if we stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.64,0:17:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.64,0:17:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, there shouldn't be\Nanything to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.10,0:17:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That guy revealed his face earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.27,0:17:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone knows it's really Taro Matsui.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.77,0:17:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Namikawa has already gone ahead\Nand told to watch the show.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.24,0:17:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Since one of us seven has to be Kira,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.49,0:17:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,that should mean\NTaro Matsui will soon be dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.78,0:18:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,-Right?\N-[Higuchi] Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.70,0:18:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the only one who knows\Nor even suspects
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.24,0:18:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,that Taro Matsui\Nisn't his real name.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.96,0:18:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That means, if I say anything,\Nit will reveal the fact that I'm Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.09,0:18:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,-[MC] That's right...\N-Yeah,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.46,0:18:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,that's true. I'll talk to you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.92,0:18:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[MC] Stay tuned to Sakura TV
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.01,0:18:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!\N[dials number]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.30,0:18:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[computer beeps]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.60,0:18:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[Soichiro Yagami] Ryuzaki, Mogi is in\Nposition in front of Yoshida Productions.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.52,0:18:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,He's just received a call from Higuchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.39,0:18:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's time for phase two.\NEverything's as planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.77,0:18:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,[Higuchi] Moji, where's Misa?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.65,0:18:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[Mogi] Oh, Mr. Higuchi,\Na pleasure to hear from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.48,0:18:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry but Misa Misa is taking\Na much-needed vacation right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.40,0:18:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,She should be back by, oh,\Ntomorrow morning though.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.86,0:18:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You can reach her then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.91,0:18:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,[Higuchi] I'm asking you\Nwhere she is now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.12,0:18:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[Mogi] Well that's private information.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.91,0:18:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,She's requested\Nthat no one know where she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.04,0:18:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very sorry. I'll have her contact you\Ntomorrow, first thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.63,0:18:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[Higuchi] Damn. I know his face.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.46,0:18:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I could kill him at any time,\Nif I only knew his name!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.76,0:18:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know if Misa's former manager was\Nan entertainer at some point?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.80,0:19:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,-Come again?\N-[Higuchi] I'm talking about Taro Matsui.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.97,0:19:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,[Mogi] Oh. I was only recently hired\N[chuckles] so I don't know much about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.89,0:19:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,If you need some information I can let you\Ntalk to someone from the office
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.85,0:19:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I just remembered, everyone's in Okinawa\Nat the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.94,0:19:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You could try calling the president,\Nthough.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.82,0:19:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,This is going exactly as I planned.\NIt's almost scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.15,0:19:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't be scared, Light.\NYou should be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.95,0:19:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,[Yagami]\NI'm patching you into Higuchi's call
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.87,0:19:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,with the president of Yoshida Productions
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.08,0:19:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[Higuchi] This is Higuchi from Yotsuba.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.79,0:19:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That manager's real name\Nisn't Taro Matsui...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.25,0:19:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not even pretending to hide\Nwhat he's asking about now, is he.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.50,0:19:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Stupid Higuchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.58,0:19:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If he's acting like that\Nit's proof he's beginning to panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.63,0:19:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what was his real name?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.21,0:19:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,[President of YP] I think it was Yamada…\NNo, wait... Yamashita.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.97,0:19:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. And his first name was…\NI'm sorry, I can't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.26,0:19:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[yelling] Don't screw with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.64,0:19:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Why the hell can't you remember\Nthe names of the people you hire?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.39,0:19:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,[President of YP] All right, no need\Nfor that kind of language.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.90,0:19:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got his personnel file\Nback at the office.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.36,0:19:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Then go back there and get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.53,0:19:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,[President of YP] You've gotta be\Nkidding me. Give me a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.32,0:20:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We're on our first company vacation\Nin two years!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.41,0:20:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you want to know that badly,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.12,0:20:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give you the pin code\Nfor the office lock.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.12,0:20:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You can go in yourself\Nand look it up, how's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.20,0:20:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The personnel files are in the desk\Nat the back to the left.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.04,0:20:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll find them filed in\Nthe bottom drawer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.92,0:20:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,They should all be sorted alphabetically.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.29,0:20:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm pretty sure it was Yamashita.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.96,0:20:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,[Higuchi] If they're going to announce\Nat the end of the program,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.88,0:20:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,that means I have two hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.68,0:20:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa] So, what's he going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.86,0:20:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,[engine revs]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.12,0:20:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[Wedy] I see Higuchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.37,0:20:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,He's only carrying a single bag.\NI'm in pursuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.04,0:20:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything is still going\Naccording to plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.04,0:20:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.01,0:21:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll kill him.\NI'll kill him no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.97,0:21:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I've come this far,\NI won't let them stop me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.26,0:21:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not giving up\Nuntil I have everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.44,0:21:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughs maniacally]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.66,0:21:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,TO BE CONTINUED
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.63,0:21:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[theme music plays]